@startuml c4_context
!theme plain

title C4 Context Diagram - Claude Skills Web UI

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

actor "User" as user <<Person>>
note right of user
  Skill author or viewer
  using a web browser
end note

rectangle "Claude Skills SPA" as spa <<Software System>> #4A90D9
rectangle "API Server" as api <<Software System>> #50C878

user --> spa : Browses, authors,\nand manages skills
spa --> api : REST API calls\nover HTTPS\n(JSON + JWT)

@enduml
